name: Paper Plane (itch) (agusuga)
description:
A small game inspired by WarioWare's Paper Plane.

Use the left and right arrow keys to control the plane. Press spacebar to start and to restart after crashing.

Let me know your best score! Mine is 91.

Music: "Getting it Done" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
